MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: Location: Station is just northeast of the middle of the southwestern arm of lake. MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: Location: Station is 2/3 the way to South Desor Campground from North Desor Campground and located between the eastern-most large island in mid-lake and the small island north of South Desor Campground.    A map with additional notes on Station Description is shown in Record #1 under the Pictures tab above.    Initial sampling station was at 47.9745156, 88.9871451 prior to 06/15/2007.  Station was moved to above location prior to 08/08/2007 sampling event.    Landmarks: 1. Southeast end of eastern large island is 246°  2. Small island to the east is 72°  3. North Desor Campground is 315°.  Images of landmarks are shown in Records #2 and 3 under the Pictures tab above.  A benchmark was established and used as a reference point by which to measure lake water level.
